'''Tikdi''' d [[uddis akruran]] yettinigen neɣ yettferfiren deg [[azwu|uzwu]] s usersiy idrusen (qlilen) s waṭas [[Tagerrawt|yessekday-it]] (yesriḥay-it) umdan neɣ uɣersiw s [[tinliwin|tnila]] n [[Asekdu|usekdu]] 

Tikdi tezmer ad tili tgerrez am tekdi n [[ajjig|ujjik]] d [[igumma]] akken i tezmer ad tili d-iri-it am tekdi n [[Alammu|ulammu]] 

Llan 7 n [[aferdis akruran|iferdisen ikruranen]] ifraren kan ssufuɣen-d tikdiwin:  Fluṛ (F), Kluṛ (Cl), Bṛum (Br), Yud (I), [[Aksujin]] (O²), Fusfuṛ (P), [[ihiǧǧ]] (As)

